data.description: Beautiful move-in ready one-story home in Travis Ranch! Built by Megatel in 2017. Open floor plan with fresh paint and new carpet in all bedrooms. Beautiful luxury vinyl plank in entry, living, dining, kitchen, bath’s & hallway. Kitchen offers built in cabinets, granite counter-tops, black appliances with smooth top electric range & pantry. Spacious owner’s retreat in the back of the home. Ensuite bath has large walk-in shower and walk -in closet with 3 level bars & a built in shoe rack. Large backyard with covered patio and no direct neighbors behind you. Wonderful community amenities include a large swimming pool, splash park, community pavilion & playgrounds. Plus a basketball court and sports fields. Conveniently located to shop and frequent Forney, Heath & Rockwall and quick access to Highway 80. Elementary School inside the subdivision. Come see today!
